figure_1: Structural equation model with the bifactor PHQ and emotion regulation strategies. Note. Only significant correlations are shown. Double-headed arrows depict correlations, whereas single-headed arrows depict factor loadings of latent variables. Red arrows indicate negative relationships. PHQ = Patient Health Questionnaire. Color image is available online only at the journal website.
